sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Master
    participant PS as Practice Service
    participant CS as Calendar Service
    participant SCHED as APScheduler
    participant NS as Notification Service
    participant U as Users (booked)
    
    Note over M,U: Practice creation with auto-reminders
    
    M->>PS: POST /practices (scheduled_at: 2025-12-28 18:00 UTC)
    PS->>PS: Create Practice record
    PS->>CS: schedule_practice_reminders(practice_id, scheduled_at)
    
    CS->>SCHED: Add job: remind_24h<br/>(run_at: 2025-12-27 18:00)
    SCHED-->>CS: Job scheduled
    
    CS->>SCHED: Add job: remind_1h<br/>(run_at: 2025-12-28 17:00)
    SCHED-->>CS: Job scheduled
    
    CS->>SCHED: Add job: remind_10m<br/>(run_at: 2025-12-28 17:50)
    SCHED-->>CS: Job scheduled
    
    CS-->>PS: Reminders scheduled ✓
    PS-->>M: Practice created
    
    Note over M,U: 24 hours before practice
    
    SCHED->>CS: Trigger: remind_24h
    CS->>NS: send_practice_reminder(practice_id, timing="24h")
    
    NS->>PS: Get practice details
    PS-->>NS: Practice data
    
    NS->>PS: Get bookings (status=confirmed)
    PS-->>NS: List of users
    
    loop For each booked user
        NS->>NS: Create Notification record<br/>(template: practice_reminder_24h)
        NS->>U: Telegram: "Practice tomorrow at 18:00!<br/>Don't forget to fill the check-in quiz"
    end
    
    Note over M,U: 1 hour before practice
    
    SCHED->>CS: Trigger: remind_1h
    CS->>NS: send_practice_reminder(practice_id, timing="1h")
    
    loop For each booked user
        NS->>U: Telegram: "Practice starts in 1 hour!<br/>Prepare your space 🧘"
    end
    
    Note over M,U: 10 minutes before practice
    
    SCHED->>CS: Trigger: remind_10m
    CS->>NS: send_practice_reminder(practice_id, timing="10m")
    
    loop For each booked user
        NS->>U: Telegram: "Practice starts in 10 min!<br/>Join: [Zoom Link]"
    end
    
    Note over M,U: Practice status change
    
    alt Master cancels practice
        M->>PS: PATCH /practices/{id} (status=cancelled)
        PS->>CS: cancel_practice_reminders(practice_id)
        CS->>SCHED: Remove jobs: remind_*
        SCHED-->>CS: Jobs removed
        CS-->>PS: Reminders cancelled
    end
